nodes.text: Caibbest Obarel was a male Human who lived during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. He made his living as a merchant for Interplanetary Component Exchange on board Carrick Station.

Caibbest Obarel first appeared in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare in 2011, as a Interplanetary Component Exchange vendor. He was later removed in Game Update 4.0 on October 20, 2015.
